<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_486" id="242v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_486_r1l1"><expan>Byſch<ex>of</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>VVircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_486_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> / Vns hat <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeÿr / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l3">vnd Ratgeſell / geſagt / vvie ewr gnad mit Jm geredt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l4">hab / als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Heincʒen <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Gıch / vnd Heincʒ Spörleins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l5"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / . vnd daʒ <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l6">daʒ vvir Jn 
<del rend="strikethrough">etlıch </del> ein cʒeit <expan>ſıchert<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . in des er cʒü vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l7">her gen 
<del rend="strikethrough">gen </del> <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> cʒe <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> be </del> cʒu <expan>beſeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> maint </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l9">ob er ſich gütlıch mit Jm <expan>gericht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> möht / . <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l10"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Seynt das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gevellıch ıſt / ſo wöllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l11">vvir Jn durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vvıllen ſıchern / vnd ſıchern Jn auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l12"><expan>hiecʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſant <expan>Laurencʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> tag <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> ſchirſt kümt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l13">für vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l14"><expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol / Jr weıſet Jn / daʒ er den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rıchte / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l15">Jn vnklaghaft mache / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_486_r1l16"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Petri et Paulȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_486" id="242v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Bysch<ex>of</ex></expan> czü <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, uns hat <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeyr,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und ratgesell, gesagt, wie ewr gnad mit im
                        geredt hab als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Heinczen
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Gich und Heincz Spörleins,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s,</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, und daz <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>maynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> wer, daz wir in ein czeit
                                <expan>sichert<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, in des er czü uns her gen
                                <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> cze <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und czu <expan>beseh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> maint, ob er sich gütlich mit im
                                <expan>gericht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> möht.
                            <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r,</expan> seynt das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gevellich ist, so wöllen wir in durch
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen sichern und sichern in auch
                            <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">sant
                                    <expan>Laurencze<ex>n</ex></expan> tag</q>10.08.1412</note></app>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        schirst kümt, für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und getrawen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, ir weiset in, daz er den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> richte und in unklaghaft mache. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Petri et
                        Pauli. </ab>
</div>
